Quote:  <i>Griselinia lucida (The Shining Broadleaf).<i> ... From 3 ft.-30 ft in height, often epiphytic. Leaves 4 in.-8 in. long, very thick, shining. ... Native name Puka. A name given to any broad-leaved tree.
